Program: Discovery
Title: The New Alchemists - part three
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxw2
Last Broadcast Date: 06 August 2001
The third of Roland Pease's explorations of the frontiers of chemistry. In this programme he examines the war against infection and visits Detroit in the US to demonstrate that it is not medics but chemists who are in the frontline in the fight against disease.